a jury convicted a christian science couple of 
manslaughter in the death of their 2yearold son in a case that 
weighed religious faith against parental responsibilities to 
provide medical care 
some jurors cried after finding ginger and david twitchell both 
34 guilty wednesday of involuntary manslaughter in the 1986 death 
of their 2yearold son robyn who suffered a bowel obstruction 
it has been hard on everyone and it was certainly hard on 
