the government ministry that helped engineer 
japans exportfueled economic boom says the global powerhouse must 
now turn inward and set its own house in order 
funding priorities once almost exclusively targeted to 
industrial growth should shift to the nations frayed 
infrastructure and frustrated consumers says the an advisory 
