french presidential spokesman hubert vedrine reported later that 
the allies had endorsed bushs idea 
however a british spokesman said prime minister margaret 
thatcher was cool toward the idea of declaring nuclear weapons as 
arms of last resort 
i think the trouble is we are concerned about the implications 
