president bush and western allies are offering 
soothing reassurances and considering a massive financial bailout 
to brace mikhail s gorbachev against an uncertain future its a 
big gamble on a soviet leader who gives himself only two more years 
to succeed or fail 
gorbachev dramatically raised the stakes for himself and the 
