said the request was not specific but expressed his hopes for 
positive conclusions at both the nato summit and the economic 
summit in houston next week which would enhance european security 
and bolster his economic reform program 
gorbachev needs a shot of western cash for a variety of reasons 
including a balanceofpayments deficit topping 2 billion half 
of that owed to west german companies and creditors and to put a 
greater variety of foodstuffs and consumer items in soviet stores 
at a time of rising domestic tensions 
