from pease air force base nh after a long workandplay weekend 
at kennebunkport maine 
in london the leaders gathered around a long oval table in a 
chandeliered room of lancaster house a government mansion 
mitterrand was late 
the weather was chilly and it rained intermittently and the 
traditional family protrait of the 16 leaders was moved indoors 
