how can anyone speak out against whats going on here said 
a 23yearold woman sitting with her baby in puerto boyacas park 
they control everything 
according to the police report the economic crisis 
confronting the selfdefense groups was resolved through an 
alliance with drug trafficking in 1985 
in return for money the private armies helped process and 
smuggle cocaine and killed opponents of drug trafficking it said 
no one including the government denies that elements of the 
colombian army initially armed and trained vigilante groups 
it was the government which created them by decree armed 
them and trained them but when convenient the government washes 
its hands of everything duque said 
the report by the secret police implicated the armed groups in a 
1988 massacre of 20 peasants in northern colombia and other 
atrocities it said they were involved in many of the 1000 murders 
since 1985 of members of the leftwing patriotic union party 
magdalena medios private armies have close ties to armed 
